overview: Hyde is nervous about getting tickets to the Led Zepelin concert. Kelso and Fez dress up as rock stars to score with groupies. Donna gets a chance to go backstage, but afterward remains strangely lip locked about the experience, which annoys and worries Eric. When Kitty forces Red to talk Mano a Mano to Eric, it doesn't help much either.
tagline: Get ready for some sex, jugs, and Rock 'N Roll -- 1970s style!
title: '70s Show: A XXX Parody
